  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业执行器控制器（ActuatorController）的IoT数据流画一张桑基图。核心流程是：传感器S的数据分成两路，一路直接到控制器C，另一路先到信号调理模块SC1。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S",
        "C",
        "SC1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，S是总入口。那SC1之后是到C汇合，还是有自己的下游路径？另外S到C和S到SC1的流量比例大概是多少？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S",
        "C",
        "SC1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SC1不直接到C，而是先到SC2做二次调理。S到C是55单位，S到SC1是45单位。然后SC1输出30到SC2，C输出50到SC2，这样SC2总共汇聚80单位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S",
        "C",
        "SC1",
        "SC2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：S分叉到C（55）和SC1（45），然后C和SC1都汇入SC2，其中SC1到SC2是30，C到SC2是50。SC2之后流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S",
        "C",
        "SC1",
        "SC2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SC2输出到网关G，流量55。这里有个损耗，SC2的输入是80，但输出55，差值25是滤波和协议转换的 overhead。然后G再到终端T，最终交付50。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SC2",
        "G",
        "T"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下数值：G到T是50，意味着G也有5单位的损耗。整个链路是 S→SC1→SC2→G→T 和 S→C→SC2→G→T 两条路径汇合，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S",
        "SC1",
        "C",
        "SC2",
        "G",
        "T"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，完全正确。两条支路在SC2汇合，体现多源数据融合的特性。用sankey-beta风格，能直观看出哪段损耗最大。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SC2",
        "sankey-beta"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已完成。图中清晰展示了从传感器S经过信号调理SC1/SC2、控制器C、网关G到终端T的完整数据流，各节点流量和损耗都标注清楚了。",
